      "status_detail": "Version 1 implements exclusive lock acquisition and orphaned-lock recovery, one exact-size lock surface per output, configure and role validation, locked-frame presentation barriers across all outputs, secure blanking, hotplug and output reconfiguration, lock-only rendering and input routing, and explicit unlock. Sandboxed security-context clients cannot see the privileged global; input-method grabs and virtual keyboards are inhibited while locked."
    },
    {
      "id": "idle-notify",
