      "status_detail": "Version 2 provides seat-scoped idle and input-idle notifications using a shared monotonic timer. Keyboard, pointer, scroll, and touch activity resume and restart matching notifications; input-idle notifications ignore inhibitors, while regular notifications track visible idle-inhibited surfaces and restart their timeout when inhibition ends."
