      "status_detail": "Stable version 2 advertises seat-scoped tablets, tools, and pads. Tool proximity, axes, tip, buttons, independent cursor surfaces, and cursor-shape-v1 integration are implemented alongside pad buttons, groups, modes, rings, strips, and version 2 dials. Pad focus follows the newest eligible tablet tool, prefers a tablet sharing the physical device, and supports standalone pads; hotplug, dynamic seat reassignment, session locking, surface destruction, and framed event delivery are handled. Feedback descriptions are accepted and intentionally ignored."
